sql:
SELECT SMN, VHI
FROM climate_data
WHERE year = (SELECT MIN(year) FROM climate_data) AND week = 1;

SELECT year, AVG(VHI) AS average_VHI
FROM climate_data
GROUP BY year;

external_knowledge:
- Best-performing in this context means the stations with the highest predicted_VHI values and the most recent last_updated_date within each region;
- The 'top three' refers to the highest-ranked stations in each region based on the criteria mentioned;
- The confidence level of predictions is considered 'High'.

